content: Immersive Program Frontend Engineering is an intensive 3 months program designed to train future frontend engineers in the fundamentals of software development. Studying Pair Programming, HTML/CSS, Git, Github, Gitflow, React, Redux, Test Driven Development,Deployment, TailwindCSS, Figma, React Typescript

During college, I was active in several organizations and served as general chairman and head of a division. Not only that, but I was also active in helping some of my lecturer's research regarding extruder machines and microcontroller data processing on websites.
